title: Zillow
description: Zillow, a leading name in the real estate industry, employs a diverse palette of blues and golds in its branding. The brand's core colors include a vibrant blue (006AFF) complemented by lighter blues (E0F2FF, A6E5FF), creating a harmonious balance representing trust and reliability. Additionally, deeper shades (0D4599, 001751) add a layer of sophistication. Touches of gold (C88205, F2A619, FFD237, FFDC69) enrich the palette, symbolizing wealth and prosperity. These colors stem from Zillow's official brand guidelines, available in their comprehensive document detailing their visual identity.
